description: Stevia Nutra Corp., a development stage company, focuses on the cultivation, development, and post-harvest processing of stevia plants for use as a sweetener. It has an agreement for the lease of 20 hectares of land in the Kampong Speu province of the Kingdom of Cambodia. The company was formerly known as AAA Best Car Rental Inc. and changed its name to Stevia Nutra Corp. in March 2012. Stevia Nutra Corp. was founded in 2010 and is based in Corner Brook, Canada.
